%5C%22%3EShahed%20waves%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20clip%20of%20the%20uncrewed%20aerial%20vehicle%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwu_samurai%2F264%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Ukrainian%20drone%20unit%20Wu%20Samurai%2C%20a%20formation%20of%20the%20117th%20Heavy%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20that%20focuses%20on%20anti-drone%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20filmed%20from%20an%20interceptor%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20a%20first-person-view%20uncrewed%20system%20designed%20to%20chase%20down%20bigger%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFootage%20from%20the%20interceptor%20showed%20the%20distinct%20chassis%20of%20a%20Gerbera%2C%20a%20propeller-driven%20drone%20designed%20to%20mimic%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-shahed-dive-bomb-shahed-kilometers-avoid-small-arms-fire-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIranian-origin%20Shahed%20loitering%20munition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20flying%20over%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20interceptor%20approaches%20the%20Gerbera%2C%20two%20optic%20cameras%20can%20be%20clearly%20seen%20attached%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Russian%20drone.%20One%20camera%20is%20aimed%20at%20the%20sky%2C%20while%20another%20is%20tilted%20toward%20the%20drone's%20rear%2C%20indicating%20that%20these%20were%20placed%20to%20detect%20threats%20from%20above%20or%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Wu%20Samurai%20Telegram%20channel%20wrote%20that%20the%20unit's%20interceptor%20successfully%20struck%20the%20Gerbera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGerbera%20got%20caught%20dodging%20with%20two%20cameras%20on%20her%20back%20%E2%80%94%20it%20didn't%20help%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20unit%20wrote.%20It's%20unclear%20exactly%20when%20and%20where%20the%20footage%20was%20filmed.%20The%20117th%20has%20been%20fighting%20in%20Donetsk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clip%20of%20the%20Gerbera%2C%20one%20of%20Russia's%20cheapest%20platforms%20that's%20now%20commonly%20seen%20in%20the%20war%2C%20is%20a%20further%20sign%20that%20Russia%20may%20be%20seeking%20to%20expand%20a%20drone%20preservation%20tactic%20that%20Moscow%20has%20been%20trying%20on%20costlier%20uncrewed%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20Ukrainian%20troops%20have%20increasingly%20reported%20encounters%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-flying-fewer-types-drones-over-ukraine-easier-to-target-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussian%20reconnaissance%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Supercam%2C%20fitted%20with%20sensors%20or%20cameras%20for%20helping%20aerial%20platforms%20dodge%20interceptors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%207%2C%20prominent%20Ukrainian%20drone%20blogger%20Serhii%20%26quot%3BFlash%26quot%3B%20Beskrestnov%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSerhii.Flash%2Fposts%2Fpfbid0KAdZJAVJqfjy2qkhB9Thp3VKaGwCj2oY4CcTwZkUkAiriyiEyiF45GgzoMG1o4Xil%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20a%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20what%20he%20said%20was%20a%20serially%20produced%20radio%20signal%20detector%20found%20on%20a%20Supercam%20drone.%20Beskrestnov%20said%20that%20once%20the%20Supercam%20detects%20an%20outside%20radio%20signal%20%E2%80%94%20which%20flags%20that%20another%20drone%20is%20likely%20nearby%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20programmed%20to%20engage%20in%20evasive%20maneuvers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20reconnaissance%20drones%2C%20that%20usually%20means%20instantly%20diving%20to%20gain%20speed%20and%20create%20distance%20from%20an%20interceptor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc61246d-6ac4-4a57-b9a8-f510d79d0be3%5C%22%3ERising%20challenges%20for%20interceptors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20recon%20drones%20such%20as%20the%20Zala%20and%20Supercam%20are%20far%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20Gerbera%2C%20one%20of%20which%20costs%20Russia%20%2410%2C000%20to%20make%2C%20according%20to%20Ukrainian%20officials'%20estimates%20in%202024.%20The%20cheap%20drone%20is%20often%20deployed%20as%20a%20decoy%20for%20the%20Shahed%2C%20and%20Russia%20launches%20it%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-machine-gunners-going-against-russian-drones-getting-new-interceptors-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehundreds-strong%20waves%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20overwhelm%20Ukrainian%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20bolstered%20its%20anti-air%20forces%20by%20developing%20low-cost%20FPV%20drones%20to%20chase%20down%20and%20crash%20into%20Shaheds%20and%20Gerberas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsidered%20a%20niche%2C%20novelty%20concept%20just%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20interceptors%20have%20been%20prioritized%20since%20late%202024%20as%20Russia%20stepped%20up%20the%20intensity%20of%20its%20Shahed%20attacks.%20Kyiv%20aims%20to%20achieve%20a%20yearly%20manufacturing%20capacity%20of%201%20million%20interceptors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wu%20Samurai's%20Tuesday%20clip%20shows%20that%20Russia%20has%2C%20in%20return%2C%20been%20equipping%20even%20its%20cheapest%20systems%20with%20evasion%20equipment%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20scale%20that%20interceptors%20are%20reaching%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20rolled%20out%20widely%20on%20long-range%20attack%20drones%20and%20decoys%2C%20the%20rear%20cameras%20and%20radio%20detectors%20could%20pose%20new%20difficulties%20for%20Ukraine's%20interceptor%20pilots.%20With%20today's%20technology%2C%20drone%20pilots%20must%20already%20be%20skilled%20enough%20to%20find%20and%20chase%20down%20Shaheds%20and%20Gerberas%20in%20a%20large%20three-dimensional%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoscow's%20shifting%20Gerbera%20tactics%20stand%20to%20produce%20implications%20beyond%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20the%20West%20also%20assesses%20how%20to%20fight%20low-cost%20uncrewed%20systems.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Poland%20and%20NATO%20said%20they%20shot%20down%20several%20Russian%20drones%20that%20illegally%20entered%20Polish%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Warsaw%20has%20disclosed%20little%20about%20the%20platforms%20and%20weapons%20used%20to%20destroy%20the%20drones%2C%20it's%20highly%20likely%20that%20the%20alliance%20deployed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-poland-russian-drones-not-the-way-ukraine-war-zelenskyy-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexpensive%20air-to-air%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20target%20Gerbera%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2018%2C%20Poland%20signed%20a%20cooperation%20memorandum%20with%20Ukraine%20that%20includes%20learning%20how%20Kyiv%20conducts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-officially-training-nato-troops-polands-drone-scare-fight-russia-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elow-cost%20air%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgerbera-back-cameras-russia-shahed-drone-war-interceptor-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758863556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d6184d5dbc4fd10da99eb0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgerbera-back-cameras-russia-shahed-drone-war-interceptor-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cameras%2C%20pointed%20at%20the%20sky%20and%20rear%20of%20the%20cheap%20Gerbera%2C%20further%20indicate%20that%20Russia%20is%20investing%20in%20wide-scale%20counters%20to%20FPV%20interceptors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgerbera-back-cameras-russia-shahed-drone-war-interceptor-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Andhra%20Constable%2C%20Home%20Guard%20'Rape%20Woman%20After%20Spiking%20Her%20Drink'%2C%20Case%20Filed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20police%20constable%20and%20a%20home%20guard%20were%20arrested%20Thursday