dent%20Donald%20Trump%20dropped%20a%20new%20round%20of%20tariffs%20on%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20heavy%20trucks%2C%20and%20furniture%20starting%20October%201.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FBrendan%20McDermid%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20announced%20new%20tariffs%20on%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20trucks%2C%20and%20some%20furniture%20starting%20October%201.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tariffs%20aim%20to%20counteract%20what%20Trump%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20unfair%20practice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20whether%20these%20tariffs%20are%20enacted%20under%20emergency%20IEEPA%20powers%20or%20Section%20232.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-immigration-prices-manufacturing-tariffs-america-economy-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etariff%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20far%20from%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20Trump%20announced%20on%20Truth%20Social%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20fresh%20flurry%20of%20tariffs%20would%20start%20on%20October%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Trump's%20post%2C%20the%20US%20will%20impose%20100%25%20duties%20on%20imported%20branded%20or%20patented%20pharmaceuticals%2C%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20heavy-duty%20trucks%2C%20and%20new%20tariffs%20on%20home%20goods%2C%20including%20kitchen%20cabinets%20and%20upholstered%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20the%20large-scale%20'flooding'%20of%20these%20products%20into%20the%20United%20States%20by%20other%20outside%20Countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20very%20unfair%20practice%2C%20but%20we%20must%20protect%2C%20for%20National%20Security%20and%20other%20reasons%2C%20our%20Manufacturing%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20posed%20on%20Truth%20Social%20that%20the%20pharmaceuticals-focused%20tariffs%20will%20apply%20to%20companies%20that%20are%20not%20building%20plants