.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-chase-fraudster-charlie-javice-says-she-cant-fly-wants-delay-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJavice%20could%20not%20safely%20fly%20to%20New%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20health%20concerns%20that%20remain%20redacted%20from%20the%20public%20record.%20She%20had%20asked%20for%20what%20prosecutors%20opposed%20as%20an%20unspecified%2C%20%26quot%3Blengthy%26quot%3B%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApplication%20denied%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20judge%20wrote%20in%20Thursday%20night's%20tersely%20worded%20final%20denial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20cited%20%26quot%3Breasons%20given%20in%20my%20prior%20order%26quot%3B%20from%20Monday%2C%20when%20he%20initially%20denied%20a%20sentencing%20delay%20and%20asked%20that%20Javice's%20lawyers%20submit%20%26quot%3Bevidence%20that%20travel%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20injurious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice's%20lawyers%20did%20supply%20more%20evidence%3A%20a%20two-page%20letter%20that%20was%20completely%20redacted%20when%20it%20hit%20the%20public%20docket%20hours%20later%20%E2%80%94%20with%20no%20indication%20of%20who%2C%20even%2C%20had%20written%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Thursday%20night's%20final%20denial%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Alvin%20K.%20Hellerstein%20said%20he%20remained%20unconvinced%20that%20Javice%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20the%20Miami%20area%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20fly%20safely%20to%20his%20Manhattan%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20remained%20%26quot%3Binsufficient%20showing%20of%20harm%20from%20a%20one-day%20appearance%20at%20sentencing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20her%20second%20request%20for%20a%20delay%3B%20the%20first%20was%20not%20opposed%20by%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%2C%2033%2C%20who%20once%20graced%20the%20Forbes%2030%20Under%2030%20list%2C%20faces%20a%20serious%20federal%20prison%20sentence%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprosecutors-recommend-charlie-javice-12-years-prison