s%20without%20fear%20of%20a%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20US%20users%20will%20still%20be%20able%20to%20watch%20videos%20from%20creators%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20White%20House%20spokesperson%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20said%20on%20Monday.%20Oracle%20will%20audit%20the%20US%20spin-off's%20algorithm%2C%20which%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bretrained%20and%20operated%20in%20the%20United%20States%20outside%20of%20ByteDance's%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Leavitt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20will%20not%20get%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-us-government-tiktok-stake-could-be-logistical-nightmare-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eequity%20stake%20in%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20government%20does%20expect%20to%20receive%20a%20fee%20for%20facilitating%20the%20sale%2C%20the%20president%20said%20on%20Friday.%20The%20Chinese%20government%20has%20yet%20to%20announce%20final%20sign-off%20on%20a%20deal%2C%20but%20Trump%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Chinese%20leader%20Xi%20Jinping%20%26quot%3Bgave%20us%20the%20go-ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20variety%20of%20questions%20remain%20about%20what%20TikTok's%20US%20business%20will%20look%20like%20after%20it%20is%20spun%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20advertising%20partners%20still%20be%20able%20to%20make%20global%20ad%20buys%3F%20What%20becomes%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-hired-amazon-staff-for-shop-pivots-back-to-china-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETikTok%20Shop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20e-commerce%20play%3F%20Do%20TikTok's%20new%20owners%20want%20to%20make%20a%20long-term%20bet%20on%20social%20shopping%2C%20or%20will%20they%20focus%20more%20on%20short-term%20revenue%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20US%20TikTok%20employees%20are%20worried%20that%20their%20new%20owners%20will%20deprioritize%20their%20team%20or%20division%2C%20or%20lay%20them%20off%20entirely%2C%20they%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20works%20out%2C%20great.%20If%20it%20doesn't%2C%20we'll%20have%20to%20look%20for%20another%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20current%20staffer%20who%20works%20in%20TikTok's%20e-commerce%20division%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20TikTok%20employee%20was%20curious%20what%20the%20sale%20would%20mean%20for%20their%20ByteDance%20stock%20after%20the%20deal%20goes%20through.%20They%20also%20wondered%20whether%20a%20%26quot%3Bretrained%26quot%3B%20algorithm%20in%20the%20US%20would%20be%20as%20good%20as%20the%20current%20one%20that%20ByteDance%20oversees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20TikTok%20prepares%20for%20its%20next%20phase%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it's%20already%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20managing%20its%20American%20audience%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%20currently%20works%20with%20TikTok's%20US%20Data%20Security%20division%2C%20USDS%20for%20short%2C%20to%20store%20TikTok's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-us-user-data-storage-project-texas-privacy-security-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20user%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20guard%20against%20potential%20data%20leakage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224c52d7df-5328-4901-91cf-f943474495c8%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20got%20here%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TikTok%20sale%20is%20the%20result%20of%20a%20multi-year%20push%20from%20Congress%20and%20Presidents%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20get%20ByteDance%2C%20a%20company%20with%20roots%20in%20China%2C%20to%20divest%20from%20TikTok's%20US%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20effort%20came%20to%20a%20head%20last%20year%20when%20Congress%20passed%20a%20law%20that%20gave%20TikTok%20until%20January%2019%20to%20find%20a%20new%20owner%20or%20face%20a%20ban.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-upheld-supreme-court-ruling-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EByteDance%20challenged%20the%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20lost.%20The%20com