gcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20that%20single%20pilot%2C%20the%20project%20has%20spread%20like%20the%20roots%20of%20a%20forest%2C%20reaching%20over%201%2C600%20villages%20with%20more%20than%20three%20million%20native%20trees%20planted.%20The%20model%20is%20as%20much%20social%20as%20it%20is%20environmental.%20TBTP%20stresses%20not%20only%20planting%20but%20also%20long-term%20care.%20Saplings%20are%20nurtured%20for%20up%20to%2030%20months%2C%20creating%20steady%20employment%20for%20local%20residents%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20women%20and%20youth%2C%20who%20make%20up%2070%25%20of%20the%20caregiving%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20happens%20after%20planting%3F%20The%20work%20that%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlanting%20is%20only%20the%20start.%20The%20real%20effort%20is%20in%20the%20care%20%E2%80%94%20watering%2C%20pruning%2C%20and%20protecting%20%E2%80%94%20until%20the%20trees%20can%20stand%20on%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20Gurpreet%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEmpowering%20youth%20through%20this%20work%20is%20important.%20It%20is%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F467221%2Freeva-sood-chemical-free-farming-empower-rural-women-agriva-naturally%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstilling%20purpose%2C%20building%20self-reliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20reshaping%20how%20communities%20view%20their%20future.%20When%20young%20people%20become%20guardians%20of%20these%20forests%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20they%20lead%20their%20communities%20towards%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Inderjit%20and%20many%20others%2C%20this%20change%20has%20become%20deeply%20personal.%20A%20seasoned%20cultivator%2C%20he%20had%20long%20watched%20his%20soil%20decline.%20He%20offered%20a%20kanal%20of%20his%20private%20land%20to%20the%20project%20with%20cautious%20optimism.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20sceptical%20at%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20tried%20planting%20before%2C%20but%20the%20trees%20didn%E2%80%99t%20survive.%20When%20Roundglass%20came%2C%20they%20stayed%2C%20cared%20for%20the%20saplings%2C%20and%20involved%20us%20in%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20land%20hosts%20a%20flourishing%20mini%20forest%20of%20nearly%20three%20kanals%20with%20over%20700%20trees%20from%20more%20than%20100%20varieties%2C%20including%20peepal%2C%20neem%2C%20and%20jhand.%20The%20impact%20has%20been%20striking.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20diverse%20forest%2C%20resilient%20and%20alive.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F410969%2Fretirement-teacher-turns-barren-hill-thriving-forest-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBirds%20have%20returned%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20crops%20have%20improved%20because%20they%20eat%20the%20pests%20naturally.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20reduced%20chemical%20sprays%2C%20and%20the%20soil%20feels%20richer.%20It%20is%20a%20gift%20to%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20his%20voice%20heavy%20with%20emotion.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20once%20questioned%20why%20I%20was%20so%20involved%20in%20The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project.%20Now%2C%20they%20come%20and%20sit%20in%20the%20forest.%20It%20is%20peaceful%20and%20has%20united%20the%20whole%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBirdsong%20and%20biodiversity%20%E2%80%93%20When%20nature%20returns%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lang%2C%20Romanpreet%20tells%20a%20similar%20story%20of%20renewal.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dry%20patch%20near%20the%20crematorium%20was%20lifeless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20TBTP%20came%20to%20our%20village%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20plant%20trees.%20It%20brought%20work%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20women%20and%20youth%20%E2%80%94%20who%20watered%2C%20tended%2C%20and%20protected%20the%20saplings.%2